gnome-control-center: gnome-control-center (GNOME Control Panel)
gnome-control-center:
gnome-control-center: The GNOME Control Center is a configuration tool for easily setting
gnome-control-center: your GNOME environment.  It allows you to configure various parts of 
gnome-control-center: your system using a collection of tools called "capplets". These 
gnome-control-center: capplets may be associated with the core set of GNOME applications or 
gnome-control-center: other applications for which the developers have written capplets.
